		<defName>AzuriPacifist</defName>
		<title>Pacifistic Grub</title>
		<titleShort>Pacifist</titleShort>
		<baseDesc>Unlike most Azuri, [PAWN_nameDef] grew up with a strong sense of empathy. Sadly this meant that [PAWN_pronoun] was unable to make meaningful connections with other Azuri. \n[PAWN_pronoun] found happiness in [PAWN_possessive] artwork despite this.
